data.description:
Rare Property with Many Uses. This Spacious 2,840 sq. ft. Home is also Zoned "Industrial" on a 24,090 sq. ft. .55 Acre Lot. Bring your RV's, Off-
Road Vehicles, Equipment or Horses. This Mountain Resort Home features 5 Bedrooms and 4 Baths, 8 Car Garage spaces with 4 Roll Up Doors. Enjoy the open Floorplan where you can kick back near the Beautiful Stone Fireplace/Wood Stove in the Family Room. The Kitchen is Updated with a Farm Sink & Spacious Pantry. Two Family Rooms, 1 upstairs & 1 downstairs. Ideal for Game Room or Video Room. Beautiful Mountain Views. Relax in the Spa on the back deck after Skiing, Horseback Riding or Off-Roading. 

You will find Central Forced Air Heat and an A/C Split unit in the Master Bedroom. 2 Car Attached Garage with 2 Separate Automatic Doors. Lots
of Room for Entertaining. The Fully Fenced Yard has an Automatic Gated Entrance and Circular Driveway. Automatic Exterior Lights and Security
Camera's. EV Charging Available in the Attached Garage and Shop.

At the Opposite Side of Property, you will find a functioning Shop which is 50' x 30' on the Ground Level. This 2-Story Building has an Office, 1/2 Bath and Additional Tool and Storage Room. You will find 220-Power, an Air Compressor, Wall Heater, a Half Bath and 3 Phase Power available at the street. The Shop could also be Converted to an ADU or used as a Warehouse. Near Big Bear Lake, Bear Mountain Resorts, Restaurants and Shopping.

Approved Plans for 480' Master Suite Addition to home.
